title: Understand Amazon KDP Best Sellers Rank (BSR)
description:
Lesson 5 - Learn what Amazon KDP Best Sellers Rank (BSR) is. Understand  how to use BSR in your Amazon Kindle Direct Publishing (Amazon KDP) low content book and no content book research, design, and business.
Presented by Jacob Bates and Barton Jeffs from The Page Planet (thepageplanet.com) and Design N Automation LLC (DNA LLC).
